---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page title="Contact" description="Need computer help in Limerick? Contact 061 Tech - local PC and laptop repair service. Email, WhatsApp, or live chat. Quick replies, no call centres. Serving Limerick city and county.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Contact</h1>
      <p class="page-intro">Got a question? Get in touch. I reply within 24 hours.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Options -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-grid">

        <div class="contact-card contact-card--primary">
          <h2>Live Chat</h2>
          <p>Quick questions? Chat with me directly.</p>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary chat-btn">Start Chat</button>
          <span class="contact-note">Usually reply within minutes</span>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card">
          <h2>WhatsApp</h2>
          <p>Send a message, photo of the problem, or voice note.</p>
          <a href="https://wa.me/?text=Hi%2C%20I%20need%20help%20with%20my%20computer" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">Message on WhatsApp</a>
          <span class="contact-note">Great for sending photos</span>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card">
          <h2>Email</h2>
          <p>For detailed questions or formal enquiries.</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@061tech.ie" class="contact-link">hello@061tech.ie</a>
          <span class="contact-note">Replies within 24 hours</span>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card">
          <h2>Book a Call</h2>
          <p>Need to talk it through? Schedule a video consultation.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Schedule Call</a>
          <span class="contact-note">Free 15-min intro call</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why No Phone -->
  <section class="section section--compact">
    <div class="container why-no-phone">
      <p><strong>Why no phone number?</strong> I focus on fixing computers, not fielding calls. Digital communication means everything is documented, nothing gets lost, and you can reach out anytime - even at 2am. I'll respond within 24 hours.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Form -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="form-section">
        <h2>Send a Message</h2>
        <p class="form-intro">Have a question that's not about booking a repair? Send me a message.</p>

        <form class="contact-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/xxxxx" method="POST">
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email *</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="subject">Subject</label>
            <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" placeholder="What's this about?">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Message *</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required placeholder="Your question or message..."></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Area -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container service-area">
      <h2>Service Area</h2>
      <p>I serve all of <strong>Limerick city and county</strong> with courier collection and delivery.</p>
      <p>Nearby counties (Clare, Tipperary, Kerry, Cork) may be possible - just ask for a quote on courier costs.</p>
      <p>For remote services (security setup, tune-ups, software), location doesn't matter - I can help anyone in Ireland.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Page>

<style>
  /* Page Header */
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .page-intro {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Contact Grid */
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Why No Phone */
  .section--compact {
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
  }

  .why-no-phone {
    max-width: 700px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why-no-phone p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .chat-btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .contact-card {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-card--primary {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .contact-card h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .contact-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .contact-note {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Form Section */
  .form-section {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .form-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .form-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .contact-form {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 500px) {
    .form-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Service Area */
  .service-area {
    max-width: 600px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .service-area h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .service-area p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
</style>
